{
  "stem": "5470.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he pulled out of his, uh, briefcase a box with all cards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And started to ask me about, is that person there?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Is that person there?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he knew-- he had instructions to approach me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And whilst we were busy doing that, a group of Jewish people [? came on. ?] And, uh-- they, uh, said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Van As, Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Van As, we-- we want you here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what they had a Dutch flag there, and they had an Oranje flag there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they got me outside and, uh, if I wanted to hoist the flag.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I hoisted the flag, then, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By singing the national anthem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, it was, uh, quite a story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Which national anthem?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they put a sash around me, Oranje-- Oranje sash.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's in, uh, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, they painted on it the date of the liberation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And actually, what's on there is the flag is mast at half.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the reason for it, on that particular day, President Roosevelt died.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But that's in, uh, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Up until the end of March 1946.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, uh, I had-- but I was asked straightaway after the liberation that by the Dutch commander of the province if I would take over the control of the camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also for the, uh, Dutch [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I came here for the Jewish people, I leave with the Jewish people, and I see that that's the finish of my task here.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, I don't want to be part of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I saw it as my task.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came there for the Jewish people and to protect them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that task was over on the moment that I brought them back home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what was the use for me staying in the camp?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
